HEADWORD: Toilful
<hw>Toil"ful</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Producing or
involving much toil; laborious; toilsome; <as>as, <ex>toilful</ex>
care</as>.</def> <rj><au>Mickle.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
